== Usage ==
<pre>
{{GitHub Link|octocat/Hello-World}}
{{GitHub Link|octocat/Hello-World|Custom Link Text}}
</pre>

== Parameters ==
* '''1''': GitHub repository path (owner/repo)
* '''2''' (optional): Custom link text. If not provided, uses the repository name.

